{"title":"快板家信","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"快板家信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士何长富，最近收到一封他舅父安佩之的来信，信上写着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“长富外甥听我言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你走后有半年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是为国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是为了打蒋介石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坏家伙顽固蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你多学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼你身体更康健。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里一切事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你不要挂念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你母也快乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不缺吃来不缺穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子也种上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里照顾也周全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你母有难困，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要关照理当然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与同志要和气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作战斗作模范，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上级命令要服从，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动干活要争先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的身体不强健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多喝汤水保平安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从你去年走了后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱村又走几十男，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南头走了徐记明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明亮那孩也参战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是英雄，好英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄都是真青年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舅父要不是年纪大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐参军去打蒋坏蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸短话长说不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万记在心里边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要是看不懂这封信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找你连长指导员给你念念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并祝你连长指导员都康健。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长富念完了他舅父的信，喜的闭不上嘴，马上就回了一封信说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“舅父，你的来信我收到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴的心里蹦蹦跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离家半年谢谢你，对我母亲照顾多周到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝我的话记得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在前线我一定爱护身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀退蒋贼把仇报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉敌人把枪缴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自卫战中立功劳！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}